      "mission_tab_content_description": "<p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed\">To allow progressive organizations to harness the power of AI, automation, and data to:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 group/item\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-accent opacity-80 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Discover new operational efficiencies and growth opportunities.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 group/item\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-accent opacity-80 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Make daily operational and decision-making simpler.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 group/item\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-accent opacity-80 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Empower teams with solutions that enhance success.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 group/item\"><div class=\"mt-1 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-accent opacity-80 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Deliver meaningful value through intelligent transformation.</span></li></ul>",
